    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-lab-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team accepted the package for submission review. All 13 credibility factors have been evaluated or flagged. The primary validation evidence (VR-001, VR-002) demonstrates NIH prediction accuracy within acceptable bounds under the 2024-q3-build-2 solver configuration. The team considers the validation results transferable to the current 2026-q1-build-7 model of record, noting that the near-wall integration update is expected to have negligible effect on bulk hemolysis predictions. Formal re-validation under the current build is recommended as a post-market commitment.",
